title: Funky Pies
typeOfFood: Vegan, Organic, Western, Fast food, Delivery, Take-out, Catering
description: Small cafe serving a variety of chunky pies in addition to cupcakes, carrot cake, chocolate cake, and banana bread - all made on the premises. The pie fillings are also available as a "pie-tato," which means the pie filling is served in a jacket potato. Organic fairtrade coffee served with Bonsoy, plus organic juice, tea. Desserts and a selection of processed vegan food items such as soy condensed milk available.
